data.description: Welcome to 7125 Fledgling Ln in the desirable Falcon Crest Subdivision in Ooltewah, TN. Situated on a corner lot with views of White Oak Mountain, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath split-level home is a perfect blend of style, space, and convenience. As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and spacious living area, seamlessly flowing into eat in kitchen for a great open feel. The three generous bedrooms ensure ample space for rest and relaxation, with the primary suite standing out as a true retreat. With a large primary bathroom and a sizable closet designed to accommodate all your storage needs. With a large laundry room conveniently placed right across from the primary bedroom laundry is made a breeze. The partially finished basement is an entertainer's dream, presenting a cozy electric fireplace set in a custom built pallet wood wall that sets the mood for any gathering. The custom-made bar is a statement piece, perfect for hosting friends and family. Adjacent to the main area, a versatile flex room awaits your creativity - ideal for a home office, gym, or additional guest room. Round out this amazing home with a large 2 car Garage with ample storage.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful split-level home your own. Contact me today to schedule a viewing and experience firsthand all this property has to offer.
